Class ErrorPattern

    • org.eclipse.cdt.core.errorparsers.ErrorPattern

    Error Pattern - used by Error Parser to convert build output to problem markers

        public ErrorPattern(String pattern,
                    int groupFileName,
                    int groupLineNum,
                    int groupDesc,
                    int groupVarName,
                    int severity)
        Full Pattern Constructor. Note that a group equal -1 means that the parameter is missing in the error message.
        Parameters:
        pattern - - regular expression describing the message
        groupFileName - - matcher group of file name
        groupLineNum - - matcher group of line number
        groupDesc - - matcher group of description
        groupVarName - - matcher group of variable name
        severity - - severity, one of
        IMarkerGenerator.SEVERITY_INFO,
        IMarkerGenerator.SEVERITY_WARNING,
        IMarkerGenerator.SEVERITY_ERROR_RESOURCE,
        IMarkerGenerator.SEVERITY_ERROR_BUILD
